IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User {{EMAIL_ADDRESS}}
PassCmd "pass show mail/gmail"
TLSType IMAPS

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/Mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/Mail/gmail/Inbox
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel gmail
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns "INBOX" "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/Trash"
Create Near
Expunge Both
SyncState *
